<p>Edit the index.markdown file.</p>

<pre><code class="ruby /about/index.markdown https://michaeljcarey.github.io Source Article">---
layout: page
title: "About Michael J Carey"
comments: true
sharing: true
footer: true
---
Ice cream is good for you because it makes you happy.
</code></pre>

